def downcast_numeric(df):
    df2 = df.copy()
    for c in df2.select_dtypes(['int64','float64']).columns:
        df2[c] = pd.to_numeric(df2[c], downcast='integer',errors='ignore')
        df2[c] = pd.to_numeric(df2[c], downcast='float', errors='ignore')
    return df2

mem_before = df.memory_usage(deep=True).sum() / 1024**2
df = downcast_numeric(df)
mem_after = df.memory_usage(deep=True).sum() / 1024**2
print(f'memory usage: {mem_before:.2f} MB -> {mem_after:.2f} MB')

memory usage: 93.90 MB -> 79.67 MB

for c in df.select_dtypes('object').columns:
    df[c] = df[c].str.strip()

candidates = [c for c in df.columns if ('date' in c.lower()) or ('arrival' in c.lower()) or ('reservation' in c.lower())]
for c in candidates:
    parsed = pd.to_datetime(df[c], infer_datetime_format=True, errors='coerce')
    if parsed.notna().sum()>0:
        df[c] = parsed
        print('Parsed as datetime:', c)

if set(['arrival_date_year', 'arrival_date_month', 'arrival_date_day_of_month']).issubset(df.columns):
    month_map = {m:i for i,m in enumerate(['January','February','March','April','May','June','July','August','September','October','November','December'],1)}
    df['arrival_date_month_num'] = df['arrival_date_month'].map(month_map)
    df['arrival_date'] = pd.to_datetime(dict(year=df['arrival_date_year'].astype(int),
                                             month=df['arrival_date_month_num'].astype(int),
                                             day=df['arrival_date_day_of_month'].astype(int)),
                                        errors='coerce')
    print('Constructed arrival_date column')

def iqr_outliers(series, k=1.5):
    q1, q3 = series.quantile([0.25,0.75])
    iqr = q3 - q1
    return (series < q1 - k*iqr) | (series > q3 + k*iqr)

outlier_counts = {c: iqr_outliers(df[c].dropna()).sum() for c in num_cols}
pd.Series(outlier_counts).sort_values(ascending=False).head(10)
